articles.author: David Slotnick
articles.title: BREAKING: Northeast Alliance turmoil as JetBlue won’t appeal end of pact, but American will - The Points Guy
articles.description: JetBlue said Wednesday that it would not appeal a recent antitrust ruling against its partnership with American Airlines, while American said it would appeal.
articles.content:
